## Business Impact

The implementation of the Data Warehouse and ETL Pipeline provides:

* Improved data quality
* Faster reporting
* Centralized analytics
* Better business visibility
* Enhanced decision-making capabilities

By consolidating data into a single source of truth, organizations can make more informed strategic and operational decisions.

---

## Conclusion

This project successfully demonstrates the complete lifecycle of a modern Business Intelligence solution, from raw data extraction and transformation to warehouse development and dashboard reporting.

The solution provides a scalable foundation for business analytics and highlights the value of ETL pipelines and data warehousing in supporting data-driven decision-making.
